#

Cottage Cheese Pancakes

25 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyEggsGluten (if using regular oats)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasyHealthyQuick

Description

Fluffy, protein-packed pancakes that are easy to make and deliciously satisfying!

Ingredients

  • cottage cheese: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2 large
  • oats (blended into flour): 1 cup
  • baking powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1/4 tsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • butter or oil (for cooking): 1 tbsp
